survey_response.review_text: (This case is an example that Normal delivery is possible even after total hip replacement surgery and c-section is not necessary)We are blessed with baby boy with normal delivery.Dr. Padmalatha is such a wonderful human being and she is very humble and friendly😊My wife had total hip replacement surgery (THR bilateral) 4years back and she conceived for the second pregnency.I was looking for a good doctor for Normal delivery and then I found Dr. Padmalatha.We started consulting her from month one and started following her instructions.She motivated and encouraged us for normal delivery and she answered all our queries without any hesitations and explained each and every point in detailed and when needed she routed experts to get their opinion as well.Hats off to her Patience and cool attitude.I would like to thank Dr. Padmadalatha for all her support 🙏🙏🙏

Dr. Padmalatha at Sparsh Hospital has been an excellent Gynecologist who extends extensive care and consultation for every patient. Her command and precision over work is beyond expectation. I cherish my pregnancy experience and the process of normal delivery for both children mostly because of the confidence that doctor instilled in me and for her proficiency and patience throughout this journey.  Thank you doctor for making the journey of motherhood a memorable one! Words cannot define our gratitude for your continued guidance.

Excellent experience. Madam was quite gentle and humble in listening to our problems and then explained the issue in such a way that even a layman can understand. In fact I haven't  seen such a doctor in my life who takes such keen interest in their patients wellbeing and advises the patient all the pros and cons of the treatment. I request all the so called patients to visit madam for their OBG problems personally and you will see a miracle in your life. Thank you madam for your wonderful advice.

I have visited Dr Padmalatha for difficulties in conceiving, I am extremely happy with the treatment given by her. I had conceived within 6 months of meeting her. It took 6 months because she has started medicine after tried all natural possible options. Her patience level to listen us and explanation of each and every detail is wonderful.
She has supported in all way even during the corona time. I have delivered 15 days before with c section. As there were no family members with us due to covid situation, the way Dr Padmalatha has supported both medically and emotionally during and after delivery is overwhelming for me and my husband.
Even the staff was very cooperative and friendly.

Dr. Padmalatha is very caring and friendly. She gives a huge mental support and just free us from all our worries and tensions. She educates patients to avoid the disease and eliminates the problems by attacking on root cause. She prescribes for only those tests which are relevant to the patient and avoid such treatment which has its side effects. She always treat patient like her own family member and advice the best treatment which cures the disease and heals the patient rapidly. She also gives awareness on several diseases, and precautionary methods to avoid. She explains very nicely the functions of the organs and pros and cons of dysfunction. During emergencies, she supports on calls and advice promptly. *** ** *** ** *** **** ************* * *** ** **********

Hi,As soon as I got pregnant we were in search of doctor. we checked in practo for gynecologist and finalized Dr. Padmalatha after considering the reviews in practo and distance from home to sparsh hospital. we were in contact with doctor throughout my pregnancy and delivery. I was diagnosed with covid during my 8 weeks pregnancy and she helped us in being positive during this time and suggested blood tests and gave confidence that it won't affect the baby growth. She was understanding the covid situation outside and in hospital and was not asking us to visit frequently for unnecessary reasons. only if it's required and in case of emergency only she told us to visit hospital. She insisted in right scan and tablets during my journey. I was having fibroids in uterus and doctor gave clear explanation about it. On any questions we had doctor would give us clear explanation and clarity on the same. Doctor was confident about normal delivery for me. During my delivery time she came on the right time and delivered baby safe. we are very Thankful to doctor for safe pregnancy and delivery. Doctor gave all confidence and my journey of delivery was smooth without any problem. I would definitely refer this doctor to have safe and happy pregnancy and delivery. the confidence the doctor gives and support during the journey will be helpful for any person. she clarifies with happy face. and would answer all our questions even asked multiple times. Thanks Dr. Padmalatha,Kavya Madhusudhan.

Giving her a right Anastasia was the task here, because after Anastasia the heart may behave differently since my mother was a cardiac patient. We somehow with the help of anaesthetist concluded the Anastasia that’s right for my Amma.

Then the surgery was performed by the doctor and it was done normally through vaginal without any C section. It was the doctors effort and my mother’s cooperation that made the surgery simple and mother recovered very soon.
